snippet.title: Squad Busters - Closed Beta Announcement!
snippet.description:
Our beloved Supercell characters come together for the first time ever! 🥳
#SquadBusters closed beta starts on February 6th until the 16th, only in Canada! 🇨🇦

Sign up here ➡️ https://squadbusters.com/
